4Geeks Academy offers a Data Science & Machine Learning course designed for beginners. Over 16 weeks, students learn Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics, preparing them for a career as a Data Analyst. The program covers predictive modeling, algorithms like decision trees, and both supervised and unsupervised learning. Classes meet three times a week with a maximum of 12 students, ensuring personalized attention. Participants receive a certificate recognized by various organizations, and no prior experience is required. Courses are available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop